freeze a tall glass
in shaker, combine:
2   dealcoholized gin
2   ginger ale
1/2 lemon juice
2   dashes celery/spicy/savory bitters
1/2 sliced plumcot (aka dino egg)
    set aside one slice for garnish
shake all vigorously over ice
pour into tall glass
fill with ice & plumcot slices from shaker
add more ice as desired
top with fentimans tonic
garnish with set-aside plumcot slices



